text: #GCCOVIDVaccineSurvey: Zone-wise analysis of @GaonConnection Survey data indicates every second surveyed rural households in the north zone was willing to pay for the #COVID19 #vaccine. In the south zone, only 33% were willing to pay for the vaccine. Read: https://t.co/UP89Bd4v4D https://t.co/QgMvpxFrkA
